<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7071] Allow for user defined Data in HBase Table &amp; ColumnFamily definitions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7071</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Allow for arbitrary user data in HBase Table &amp;amp; Column Family definitions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use case:&lt;br/&gt;
Allowing multiple applications to dynamically access data in HBase tables and fetch schema information from table or column family directly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
